sbt // Start session

show settings
show name
show scalaVersion
show organization

apply settings
set organization := "BlaBlub"  
set version :="2.8-SNAPSHOT"

session save // save session

compile // compiles project

~compile // compiler waits for file changes and recompiles if saved YAY

console // starts scala console BUT with ALL files from Project and Third party libs

Add third party lib:
add the line "libraryDependencies += 'THIRDPARTYLIB'" to the 
build.sbt file